				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13969695#post-4862497</guid>
				<title>+1</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13969695/scp-5623#post-4862497</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Jan 2021 05:04:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Dr Hajovsky</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>7041744</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Fun and interesting read. Really liked the mental image of a massive ship floating through space collecting dying stars piloted by a cosmic-void-being named Glen. The wrap up with the reveal that Glen has been the one to reset the universe was also fun and thought provoking. This definitely earns an upvote. Also, &quot;Star Euthanizer&quot; is such a cool name!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
